text: Prosopocera undulata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Schwarzer in 1929. It is known from Tanzania and Malawi.BioLib.cz - Prosopocera undulata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Prosopocerini Category:Beetles described in 1929
title: Prosopocera undulata
